19. exf5 e4 { The typical clearing sacrifice. } 20. Nxe4 Nxe4 21. Bxe4 Qf6
{ With excellent compensation for Black, who has absolute control over the dark squares. He will continue with ...Bd7, ...Rae8-e5 and so on. }
